	//PixRadius2DWave = sqrt((cos(HorizontalTilt*pi/180)*(p-BeamCenterX))^2 + (cos(VerticalTilt*pi/180)*(q-BeamCenterY))^2)
//	need to use new function... NI1T_TiltedToCorrectedR(TiltedR,SaDetDistance,alpha)
